## 9. CLEANUP REQUIRED BEFORE NEW FEATURES

The following must be resolved before any new channel feature is built on top of this system:

1. **Fix [assignAdmin](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/server/src/features/channels/channel.controller.js#557-647) membership guard** — change `!isMember` to `!_isTargetMember` (one character fix, critical correctness)
2. **Fix [removeChannelMember](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/server/src/features/channels/channel.controller.js#270-304) filter** — rewrite the member filter to use new format `m.user._id.toString()` instead of `String(m)`
3. **Resolve dual socket room naming** — standardize on `channel:<id>` throughout (controller emissions must match socket handler room joins)
4. **Remove or gate [joinChannelViaLink](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/server/src/features/channels/channel.controller.js#1165-1270) private channel bypass** — add `if (channel.isPrivate) return 403` guard
5. **Remove `io.emit()` in [updateChannel](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/client/src/services/channelService.js#17-19)** — replace with `io.to(`workspace_${workspaceId}`).emit(...)` 
6. **Add `unique: true` to workspace+name index** — enforce channel name uniqueness at the DB layer
7. **Add `maxlength` to `channel.name`** — prevent excessively long names
8. **Reconcile or delete dead frontend API methods** — [leaveChannel](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/client/src/services/channelService.js#26-28), [addMember](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/client/src/services/channelService.js#32-34), [getAllChannels](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/client/src/services/channelService.js#8-10), [getPublicChannels](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/client/src/services/channelService.js#11-13) in [channelService.js](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/client/src/services/channelService.js) call non-existent or wrong endpoints
9. **Split [ChannelsPanel](file:///Users/thrishankkuntimaddi/Documents/Chttrix/ChttrixCollab/client/src/components/layout/panels/ChannelsPanel.jsx#11-516) polling into a proper socket subscription** — remove the 30-second interval; rely on socket events for real-time updates
10. **Deduplicate `threadParent` vs `parentId`** on the Message schema — pick one and migrate the other

